OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright day with
OL,6,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells and
OL,7,Ffeeling very warm or hot. Low cloud
OL,8,Fand mist near the north coast slowly
OL,9,Fburning off.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight. Some bright or
OL,13,Fsunny spells at first in the evening,
OL,14,Fturning cloudier around the coasts
OL,15,Fovernight, some clear spells inland.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy at first but
OL,18,Fwith a few sunny spells. Cloud will
OL,19,Fgradually break up through the day to
OL,20,Fallow more bright or sunny spells.
OL,21,FRemaining dry and very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
